snippet.title: Team Sonic Racing - E3 Trailer
snippet.description:
E3 is almost here! Team Sonic and Team Dark race across Wisp Circuit in our latest trailer, featuring a sample of the new theme song by Crush 40!

Race with your closest friends - or against them - in Team Sonic Racing, developed by SUMO Digital and featuring a cast of characters in the Sonic universe.

You can find out more about the game at: www.TeamSonicRacing.com
